Package: autorecipes
Title: Automate your recipe planning
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2021-09-29
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Zhang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dyzhang32@gmail.com")
Description: The goal of autorecipes is to automate my weekly recipe planning. 
autorecipes achieves this by taking care of: 1. Creating and storing a database 
of recipes, 2. Customizing weekly meal plans and 3. Generating shopping lists of 
ingredients.
